Usage: off [-p] [-r] [-s] [-h] [-?] [--help]

Saves date to the file: ~/log/offtime.log and shuts the computer down (if no options are specified)

Options:
 -h,-?,--help	display this help and exit
 -p		shuts the computer down (default option)
 -r, --reboot	reboot
 -s, --suspend	suspend

Exit status:
 0	if OK
 1	if the argument is not recognised
